The x Isa object
  Has s1 "this is a string that contains enough characters to test with".
  Has s2 "a word".
End The x.

The l Isa location
End The l.

Start At l.
 Strip First 10 Character From s1 Of x.
 Say s1 Of x.	-- " contains enough ..."
 Say s2 Of x.	-- "s"
 Strip Last 3 Character From s1 Of x Into s2 of x.
 Say s1 Of x.	-- "contains enough characters to test w"
 Say s2 Of x.	-- "ith"
 Strip Last 100 Word From s1 Of x.
 Say s1 Of x.	-- ""
 Say s2 Of x.	-- "ith"
